<BaseLayout title="Privacy — Janaushdhi" description="Janaushdhi privacy policy. No ads, no tracking, minimal data.">
  <div class="page prose">
    <span class="pill">Legal</span>
    <h1 style="margin-top:12px;">Privacy policy</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated 2026-06-22.</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>Janaushdhi is a static website. We do not collect personal information, run advertising trackers, or use third-party analytics that fingerprint visitors.</p>

    <h2>Server logs</h2>
    <p>Our hosting provider (Cloudflare) maintains short-lived access logs containing IP addresses and request paths for abuse prevention. These are not linked to any identity and are rotated per Cloudflare's standard retention.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We do not set tracking cookies. The site functions without JavaScript or cookies enabled.</p>

    <h2>External links</h2>
    <p>Pages link to <a href="https://www.janaushadhi.gov.in/" rel="noopener external">janaushadhi.gov.in</a> and other government resources. Their privacy practices are governed by their own policies.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about privacy? <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
